    "description": "进入《Junkcity Factory》的世界，这是一款将工业与创造力结合的动态模拟游戏。通过29台强大的机器、33名工人和近300种独特物品，你将在一个繁忙的工厂环境中将废料转化为有价值的产品。<br><br>在一个充满活力的中型城市中，《Junkcity Factory》挑战你收集数百种不同的废料，管理33名工人并监督他们的工资，同时运营一家完全互动的工厂。优化每位工人的效率以最大化利润，同时观察库存中的每一件物品如何与真实物理规则互动——无论是掉落、堆叠还是沿生产线移动。<br><br>你的工厂是运营的核心，每个流程都需要精细调整以取得成功。从回收再利用到制造，从管理劳动力到在Junkcity商店销售产品，你的每一个决策都将影响最终收益。<br><br>你能成为终极工业大亨吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/c043353d3b8068c32674d1ae9ef3677f.poster.avif?t=1734335782\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/c043353d3b8068c32674d1ae9ef3677f.webm?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/c043353d3b8068c32674d1ae9ef3677f.mp4?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/b6af05d8b8e414e07a3b92da3f35fcf8.poster.avif?t=1734335782\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/b6af05d8b8e414e07a3b92da3f35fcf8.webm?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/b6af05d8b8e414e07a3b92da3f35fcf8.mp4?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/2f3f32efc8e7f6c1a110fa060922b20c.poster.avif?t=1734335782\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/2f3f32efc8e7f6c1a110